you must install the Rawview tool.

then,
 
type:
	make all if you are under LINUX
or 
	gmake -f Makefile.sgi if you are under SGI



for launching the programm with graphical interface, type
	viewer 

for launching the programm without graphical interface, type
	viewer -t ARG1 ARG2 ARG3
where 
	ARG1 corresponds to the first mesh (file ".raw")
	ARG2 corresponds to the second mesh (file ".raw")
	ARG3 corresponds to the sampling step

